Thanks for downloading migasfree server.

Execute: python setup.py install

Or create migasfree-server package (recommended option):

1.- Execute bin/create-package script

    $ cd bin
    $ ./create-package


2.- Install package and its dependencies:

    # dpkg -i migasfree-server_x.x-x_all.deb
    # apt-get -f install


3.- Check migasfree/settings.py (/usr/shared/pyshared/migasfree/settings.py):

    * Database parameters
    * Secret key
    * Organization name
    * Time zone
    * ...

    Override or include settings at /etc/migasfree-server/settings.py


4.- Execute this script to create initial data (default superuser is admin:admin):

    # migasfree-server-from-scratch


And enjoy migasfree experience!!!
